    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/c542252e3361bec16c14fb4d62b17c30_1614328956774960016.png",
                "key": "清风散花词",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "清风散花词"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">步天梯</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">闲云冲击波</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">步天梯</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方执行「切换角色」行动时：</span>少花费1个元素骰。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：1（可叠加，最多叠加到2次）</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">闲云冲击波</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方切换到所附属角色后：</span>造成1点风元素伤害。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：1（可叠加，最多叠加到2次）</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/1ae8071c4cb74f8e72aed923c32f88b9_6265135401096448102.png",
                "key": "朝起鹤云",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "朝起鹤云"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素伤害</span>，治疗所有我方角色1点，生成手牌<span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">竹星</span>。</p><p>（装备有<span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">竹星</span>的角色可以使用特技：<span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">仙力助推</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/800d96df9df0510eebd45f0be22e6bd7_356284104242751793.png",
                "key": "暮集竹星",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "暮集竹星"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">装备牌</span></p><p>特技：<span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">仙力助推</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span></p><p>（角色最多装备1个「特技」）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/c91f35411606350c7340492100653c9a_1237884179418430492.png",
                "key": "竹星",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [
                  {
                    "description": "",
                    "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/82c711b2a1c8eb2bb4bc97a0f6f3aeb3_8468833139057151619.png"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "竹星"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">特技</span></p><p>治疗所附属角色2点，并使其下次普通攻击视为<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">下落攻击</span>，伤害+1并且技能结算后造成1点<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">风元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/86aca81360030e82c4bb78a54f9abeab_3597803471386516778.png",
                "key": "仙力助推",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "仙力助推"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（冰）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点冰元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（水）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点水元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（火）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点火元素伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">风元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">扩散（雷）</span>：对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点雷元素伤害</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/c9c276c51fc564e26186c68343787a91_7183607067494944163.png",
                "key": "风元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "风元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">下落攻击</span></strong></p><p>角色被切换为「出战角色」后，本回合内的下一个战斗行动若为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「普通攻击」</span>，则被被视为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「下落攻击」</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">特技</span></strong></p><p>出战角色装备有「特技」卡牌时，就可以使用对应的「特技」。</p><p>使用「特技」是一种「战斗行动」。角色因冻结、石化、眩晕等原因无法使用技能时，也会同时无法使用「特技」。</p><p>角色使用「特技」时不视为使用技能，无法触发「使用技能后」「角色引发元素反应后」等效果；角色使用「特技」造成的伤害不被视为角色造成的伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/02/15/59155606/3b5977f18d39185ac0bc802fa291fb5f_6619739332025771706.png",
